subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
lead_paragraph: Nick Johnson’s blocked shot against David Stockton was emblematic of the way the No. 1-seeded Wildcats overwhelmed eighth-seeded Gonzaga to advance to the Round of 16.
